Rating: 3
I made this for a dinner party I threw and it was a success! My guests scarfed it down... I decided to serve it with a vanilla bean gelato and it made the sauce even better- the combination of the hot and cold was perfect! And the biscuits soaked up the gelato so nicely. I will definitely be making this again in the future.

