I made this last Christmas for a luncheon dessert. It went over extremely well.

Rating: 3
I made this for a Sunday brunch and it was very good--the shortcakes have a wonderful texture and work very well with the sauce. Next time I'll make sure my pears are very good quality, and I'll use less brandy--it overpowered the dish. But we still enjoyed it very much.